<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Uploads Complete - <%= formName %></title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; max-width: 600px; }
        .header { background-color: #1c3260; color: #ffffff; padding: 15px 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0; }
        .content { padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-top: none; border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px; }
        .details { background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .details p { margin: 5px 0; }
        .label { font-weight: bold; color: #555; }
        .success-text { color: #2e7d32; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.1em; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h2 style="margin: 0;">File Uploads Completed</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello <%= residentName %>,</p>
        
        <p>This is to confirm that <strong>all your files have been successfully uploaded</strong> for the following submission.</p>

        <div class="details">
            <p><span class="label">Form Name:</span> <%= formName %></p>
            <p><span class="label">Submission ID:</span> <%= submissionId %></p>
            <p><span class="label">Total Files Uploaded:</span> <%= totalFiles %></p>
            <p><span class="label">Date:</span> <%= dateStr %></p>
        </div>

        <p class="success-text">✓ Everything is complete and securely saved.</p>
        
        <p style="font-size: 0.9em; color: #666; margin-top: 30px;">
            Thank you,<br>
            Premium Properties System
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
